  "description": "Maximum layers, maximum fold amount, zero symmetry, fold point at 0.18 — near the zero crossing. At this setting the waveform folds repeatedly upon itself before it can complete a single cycle. The sound is aggressive, complex, and unstable — different for each note, each velocity. Controlled destruction. Paper torn slowly.",
